{"id":"813743116716736512","type":"text","timestamp":1776045910,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/813743116716736512","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":false,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://ouppygirlcity.tumblr.com/post/810941758966005760/i-did-my-comment-and-you-should-to-be-advised\">ouppygirlcity</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/yet-another-heathen/810932998668238848\">yet-another-heathen</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/evergreen-femme/810928248739528704\">evergreen-femme</a>:</p><blockquote><p>im so fucking scared i&rsquo;m going to throw up. its not just the court decision. read this, if you dare.</p><p class=\"npf_link\" data-npf='{\"type\":\"link\",\"url\":\"https://theneedlenews.com/anti-trans-hate-groups-petitioning-fda-for-registry-of-trans-women-crackdown-on-transition-newly-revealed-document-shows/\",\"display_url\":\"https://theneedlenews.com/anti-trans-hate-groups-petitioning-fda-for-registry-of-trans-women-crackdown-on-transition-newly-revealed-document-shows/\",\"title\":\"Anti-trans hate groups petitioning FDA for registry of trans women, crackdown on transition, newly revealed document shows\",\"description\":\"In the short term, this is not as dangerous as an outright ban on estrogen. If implemented and then combined with other methods of suppressi\",\"site_name\":\"The Needle\",\"poster\":[{\"media_key\":\"622472f552f0a9a32421ef8d103ec459:168696f1320f756c-54\",\"type\":\"image/png\",\"width\":1600,\"height\":900}]}'><a href=\"https://theneedlenews.com/anti-trans-hate-groups-petitioning-fda-for-registry-of-trans-women-crackdown-on-transition-newly-revealed-document-shows/\" target=\"_blank\">Anti-trans hate groups petitioning FDA for registry of trans women, crackdown on transition, newly revealed document shows</a></p></blockquote><p>Unlike the vast majority of anti-trans legislation, hate groups are attempting to pass these restrictions without the public at large knowing they exist. <b>This secrecy is far more insidious, and needs to be immediately addressed. </b></p><p class=\"npf_quote\">If you want to help, the two things that will make the most impact are SPREADING AWARENESS, and participating in PUBLIC COMMENT while it is still open.</p><h1>‼️<a href=\"https://www.regulations.gov/commenton/FDA-2025-P-7321-0001\">LINK TO FDA COMMENT PAGE</a>‼️</h1><h2>Document: FDA-2025-P-7321</h2><p>As of the time this article was written, <b>ALL</b> public comments were from hate groups in support of this registry. <i>Every single comment in opposition will help.</i></p><div class=\"npf_row\"><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"1904\" data-orig-width=\"1080\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/dfbf30cf0df41ac642d8783494b63fac/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-5d/s640x960/9001a5f5038a872b3e1f56180d9854bb89864279.png\" data-orig-height=\"1904\" data-orig-width=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/dfbf30cf0df41ac642d8783494b63fac/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-5d/s75x75_c1/14b3bfccd2796e57474ebf44f88707d0cedd4e7a.png 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/dfbf30cf0df41ac642d8783494b63fac/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-5d/s100x200/b55358275a714f2c11a05d3e7281aa7f00c6ae19.png 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/dfbf30cf0df41ac642d8783494b63fac/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-5d/s250x400/530a639f3a3c95fd35d596b6ce0ab455f2593474.png 227w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/dfbf30cf0df41ac642d8783494b63fac/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-5d/s400x600/287b2643b717f0bd47555944ed104da3de993b1c.png 340w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/dfbf30cf0df41ac642d8783494b63fac/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-5d/s500x750/e247f5ecb5d879fd2071b7f7f529af1280617181.png 425w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/dfbf30cf0df41ac642d8783494b63fac/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-5d/s540x810/91d822056a1ebe0c1fc0cdc66c249d149fccb798.png 459w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/dfbf30cf0df41ac642d8783494b63fac/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-5d/s640x960/9001a5f5038a872b3e1f56180d9854bb89864279.p