g-width=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/e3dd008483d1dbfbd1a40a57539d6368/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-55/s75x75_c1/dd0aa7fe9dedf31d9837a5f6bfc10186670a3df2.png 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/e3dd008483d1dbfbd1a40a57539d6368/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-55/s100x200/bf7430ef37a3d5b855059dcef9f9f690a15297a4.png 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/e3dd008483d1dbfbd1a40a57539d6368/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-55/s250x400/1b734f69b244cadb847441f34e0c580c0e415bab.png 230w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/e3dd008483d1dbfbd1a40a57539d6368/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-55/s400x600/90f4c387cd5178ab2a97e80b7cf8ef16552809cf.png 345w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/e3dd008483d1dbfbd1a40a57539d6368/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-55/s500x750/c814f48b2fa67437b90e96577e9ce9a8829316ad.png 431w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/e3dd008483d1dbfbd1a40a57539d6368/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-55/s540x810/7b7b9a06145ee61b5dfc8f7a9ec40582267f1883.png 466w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/e3dd008483d1dbfbd1a40a57539d6368/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-55/s640x960/931fd98403ea2892bc60bf2b0cdcb44fdd4e7ffd.png 552w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/e3dd008483d1dbfbd1a40a57539d6368/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-55/s1280x1920/08d83f08457413a183270592a7b1202411a46349.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"/></figure><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"1506\" data-orig-width=\"1079\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/9b639222390b80f132a3288725ff1e86/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-1a/s640x960/dfcd90e59b36c1bdb1b93494b582b9cfa81f42f7.png\" data-orig-height=\"1506\" data-orig-width=\"1079\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/9b639222390b80f132a3288725ff1e86/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-1a/s75x75_c1/f175107a4463cd1257cac87b5e9f764cda754fed.png 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9b639222390b80f132a3288725ff1e86/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-1a/s100x200/16a6f462ce10f5ee17a8985dc727182b44b3b74b.png 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9b639222390b80f132a3288725ff1e86/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-1a/s250x400/dd0899848bd397bde8aa21fc57027a8b41ff8ad4.png 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9b639222390b80f132a3288725ff1e86/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-1a/s400x600/46c99b0bd35c6bc74b689c612c2367965daa2398.png 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9b639222390b80f132a3288725ff1e86/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-1a/s500x750/804c22be0451e97412f37d068053432ea0dc2b63.png 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9b639222390b80f132a3288725ff1e86/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-1a/s540x810/74d0f73e670abcda039b69a53cc95562f5aab82f.png 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9b639222390b80f132a3288725ff1e86/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-1a/s640x960/dfcd90e59b36c1bdb1b93494b582b9cfa81f42f7.png 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9b639222390b80f132a3288725ff1e86/03bb7e0a1f28d22c-1a/s1280x1920/6eb89b0adb5a91dc47656d7696a870ce4a6510e2.png 1079w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1079px) 100vw, 1079px\"/></figure></div><blockquote class=\"npf_indented\"><p><b>Disclaimer:</b> This article is very guilty of intersex erasure, despite the fact that intersex people of all ages would be affected by these regulations the same way trans women are. However, as this is the most comprehensive and direct article currently available, it should still be widely distributed, for the sake of trans women, nonbinary people, and intersex people who will all be affected should it pass.</p></blockquote></blockquote><p>I did my comment, and you should to! Be advised that when making a comment like this on a proposed regulation, the depth of your statement does matter. I strongly encourage you to take the time to read this article to get informed on what this proposal entails, and write a detailed response concerning one or two aspects that you believe you can write cohesively about and prepare a sensible counter-argument; try to draw from other sources if you can, even if you&rsquo;re just quoting other articles in support and in defense of HRT and transfeminism. I encourage everyone to review this official list of what they&rsquo;re expecting from a quality comment.</p><div class=\"npf_row\"><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"803\" data-orig-width=\"1438\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/c03e21fe8d49104a243a34399e085b7b/3b72a157578725a0-64/s640x960/1a5983f2a16c59ddcef2531923c453950ecfd7e5.png\" data-orig-height=\"803\" data-orig-width=\"1438\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/c03e21fe8d49104a243a34399e085b7b/3b72a157578725a0-64/s75x75_c1/e170211c47cd82b0dcc3983cbbaf677ec6b64c2d.png 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/c03e21fe8d49104a243a34399e085b7b/3b72a157578725a0-64/s100x200/3549ab32924eeafa0aacebb46f7d710541742510.png 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/c03e21fe8d49104a243a34399e085b7b/3b72a157578725a0-64/s250x400/7fa3d796a8a88b7f620ced5278e5e6d88f433315.png 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/c03e21fe8d49104a243a34399e085b7b/3b72a157578725a0-64/s400x600/8391cb15f25dadfb2b988826d91e0892f1ac9a20.png 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/c03e21fe8d49104a243a34399e085b7b/3b72a157578725a0-64/s500x750/8cb44388dd170b71dffa36e5d943981e3e78fc74.png 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/c03e21fe8d49104a243a34399e085b7b/3b72a157578725a0-64/s540x810/2d020908a8bf6d894219b3524cb8001972db3d94.png 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/c03e21fe8d49104a243a34399e085b7b/3b72a157578725a0-64/s640x960/1a5983f2a16c59ddcef2531923c453950ecfd7e5.png 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/c03e21fe8d49104a243a34399e085b7b/3b72a157578725a0-64/s1280x1920/3fc8ee6427196fc20d03e117c1a999248c92bd3a.png 1280w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/c03e21fe8d49104a243a34399e085b7b/3b72a157578725a0-64/s2048x3072/13a8902339c2a67e4bb9d43cca4e5977bb8ffe8a.png 1438w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"/></figure></div><p>Remember, all public comments may have been from this hate campaign at the time of posting, but it was only 60. I know plenty of Discord servers bigger than that, let&rsquo;s show that we outnumber this hate and that we&rsquo;re gonna outlive this nightmare.</p></blockquote>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"evergreen-femme","active":true,"theme":{"header_full_width":1280,"header_full_height":426,"avatar_shape":"square","background_color":"#000000","body_font":"Helvetica Neue","header_bounds":"","header_image":