 of trans women, crackdown on transition, newly revealed document shows</a></p>","content":"<p>im so fucking scared i&rsquo;m going to throw up. its not just the court decision. read this, if you dare.</p><p class=\"npf_link\" data-npf=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;link&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://theneedlenews.com/anti-trans-hate-groups-petitioning-fda-for-registry-of-trans-women-crackdown-on-transition-newly-revealed-document-shows/&quot;,&quot;display_url&quot;:&quot;https://theneedlenews.com/anti-trans-hate-groups-petitioning-fda-for-registry-of-trans-women-crackdown-on-transition-newly-revealed-document-shows/&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Anti-trans hate groups petitioning FDA for registry of trans women, crackdown on transition, newly revealed document shows&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;In the short term, this is not as dangerous as an outright ban on estrogen. If implemented and then combined with other methods of suppressi&quot;,&quot;site_name&quot;:&quot;The Needle&quot;,&quot;poster&quot;:[{&quot;media_key&quot;:&quot;622472f552f0a9a32421ef8d103ec459:168696f1320f756c-54&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:1600,&quot;height&quot;:900}]}\"><a href=\"https://theneedlenews.com/anti-trans-hate-groups-petitioning-fda-for-registry-of-trans-women-crackdown-on-transition-newly-revealed-document-shows/\" target=\"_blank\">Anti-trans hate groups petitioning FDA for registry of trans women, crackdown on transition, newly revealed document shows</a></p>","is_root_item":true},{"blog":{"name":"yet-another-heathen","active":true,"theme":{"header_full_width":900,"header_full_height":1333,"avatar_shape":"circle","background_color":"#620C45","body_font":"Helvetica Neue","header_bounds":"","header_image":"https://64.media.tumblr.com/7568dc3dde9f6735a01fcc7b10aee2fa/53a48f83845f8650-54/s900x1333/cb07025d9d47835c51d67b497280dd92ef577cf1.jpg","header_image_focused":"https://64.media.tumblr.com/7568dc3dde9f6735a01fcc7b10aee2fa/53a48f83845f8